Package: step-sds
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Secret Discovery Service (SDS)
   step-sds is a gRPC server that implements Envoy's secret discovery service
   (SDS) to stream TLS certificates to gRPC clients like Envoy.
